repos.name: core_project_task_management
repos.description: The Task Manager system is a web application designed to facilitate task management within the context of users and administrators. It provides a user-friendly interface for users to create, update, and delete their tasks, and edit their profile. while administrators have additional privileges to manage users and their own tasks as well.

repos.name: Corona_Management_System
repos.description: The Corona Management System for Health Funds was developed to streamline the management of COVID-19 related information among members of health funds. This system provides comprehensive features for tracking vaccination records, managing member data, and monitoring pandemic-related data.

repos.name: Search_jobs_system
repos.description: The job search system is an advanced platform for connecting job seekers with suitable jobs. The system offers users a personal and efficient approach to searching for a variety of jobs and sending resumes. In addition, it allows users to post jobs, giving them the opportunity to attract potential candidates and fill vacancies.
